*rhide-1.5.20050823 (29 Aug 2005)

  29 Aug 2005; Martin Schlemmer <azarah@gentoo.org>
  +files/rhide-1.5.20050823-amd64-support.patch, +rhide-1.5.20050823.ebuild:
  Update snapshot and do a few needed cleanups.

